  + [row_002_same_frame_locality] is whether the project object lives on the same ball or cylinder as the regularity test
    = project_status: same_ball_for_source_estimate for the source estimate, but regularizing cylinder admission remains unproved
    = accepted_quantity_match: conditional
    = reason: the source has active balls and localized pressure balls, but the audit records no bridge from active ball to accepted epsilon-regularity cylinder
    = missing_conversion_lemma: active_ball_selection_yields_CKN_or_pressure_criterion_cylinder_with_matching_scale
  + [row_003_velocity_partner] is the velocity quantity required alongside pressure control
    = project_status: endpoint_global_L3_with_local_entropy_terms
    = accepted_quantity_match: mismatched_for_local_epsilon
    = reason: endpoint L3 continuation and local epsilon regularity are different targets; the current route has not extracted local velocity smallness in the same frame
    = missing_conversion_lemma: local_entropy_and_tail_budget_imply_scale_invariant_velocity_pressure_smallness
  + [row_004_pressure_size_vs_pressure_work] is whether pressure-work absorption is enough
    = project_status: pressure_work_bound_and_tail_budget
    = accepted_quantity_match: mismatched
    = reason: existing audit explicitly separates pressure-work absorption from pressure-size or oscillation smallness
    = missing_conversion_lemma: pressure_work_absorption_implies_pressure_size_smallness_under_verified_localization
  + [row_005_pressure_criterion_target] is whether pressure-bound regularity criteria are a better first target than ESS
    = project_status: promising_precheck
    = accepted_quantity_match: closest_family
